Background

		Mr. Brandon Tolany has been Senior Vice President of Worldwide Sales at Silicon Laboratories Inc. since January 4, 2016. Mr. Tolany serves as Chief Sales and Marketing Officer and Senior Vice President at Freescale Semiconductor, Inc. He is responsible for Freescale’s global sales and marketing activities. Mr. Tolany served as Chief Sales & Marketing Officer and Senior Vice President for Freescale Semiconductor, Ltd. since September 2013 until 2015. He served as Vice ... President of global marketing for Microcontrollers at Freescale from April 2013 to September 2013. From 2008 to March 2013, he served as Director of Sales and Field Application Engineers for Freescale’s Americas West Region. He started his career at Freescale (Motorola) in 2004 as a marketing manager for the i.MX applications processor product line. He served as Director of sales & business development for Luminent where he led global marketing efforts and he served as a Product Manager of Mitsubishi Electric. He holds a bachelor’s degree in communications from the University of Texas at Austin.Read Full Background




